<section class="soct soct--galeria soct-wrap soct-wrap--compressed soct-layout-gallery soct-layout-gallery--gallery_bottom_txt_top"><div class="soct-text"><div class="soct-meta"><span class="soct-taxline"><a href="https://puntoedu.pucp.edu.pe/vida-universitaria/">Vida universitaria</a> / <a href="https://puntoedu.pucp.edu.pe/tema/cultura-y-creacion/">Cultura y creación</a></span></div><h1 class="soct-title">De Evangelion a Perfect Days: anime, cine y nuevas narrativas para repensar el Japón contemporáneo</h1><div class="soct-date-below-title"><time class="soct-date" datetime="2025-11-18T16:07:15-05:00">18.11.2025</time></div></div><div id="hero-carousel-113149-6a45b295a0d97" class="soct-hero" data-hc="root" data-hc-loop="0" data-hc-autoplay="0" data-hc-delay="5000" role="region" aria-roledescription="carousel" aria-label="Carrusel destacado" tabindex="0"><div class="soct-hero__viewport"><div class="soct-hero__slides has-caption" data-hc-track><figure class="soct-hero__slide is-active" data-hc-slide data-index="0" aria-hidden="false" style="--bg:url('https://files.pucp.education/puntoedu/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/18123731/web-1920x1080-Simposio-Estudios-Japoneses-1-abre-scaled.webp');"><img src="https://files.pucp.education/puntoedu/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/18123731/web-1920x1080-Simposio-Estudios-Japoneses-1-abre-scaled.webp" srcset="https://files.pucp.education/puntoedu/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/18123731/web-1920x1080-Simposio-Estudios-Japoneses-1-abre-scaled.webp 1600w, https://files.pucp.education/puntoedu/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/18123731/web-1920x1080-Simposio-Estudios-Japoneses-1-abre-300x169.webp 300w, https://files.pucp.education/puntoedu/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/18123731/web-1920x1080-Simposio-Estudios-Japoneses-1-abre-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://files.pucp.education/puntoedu/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/18123731/web-1920x1080-Simposio-Estudios-Japoneses-1-abre-768x432.webp 768w, https://files.pucp.education/puntoedu/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/181237